    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of honest, road-worn character that turns heads for all the right reasons\u2014a machine with stories behind it and plenty of life left for the next owner with vision. It\u2019s an ideal pick for someone looking for an affordable set of wheels, a practical project, or a dependable companion for around-town duty. There\u2019s a raw charm here you just don\u2019t get from cookie-cutter options, and at this price, it opens the door to opportunity for the buyer who sees potential where others only see age.",
