      "description": "Clean, honest, and priced to move, this vehicle is a smart choice for anyone seeking affordable transportation without unnecessary hype. It shows its age and is best suited for a buyer who values straightforward value, whether as a budget commuter, spare vehicle, or practical project. A great opportunity to get into a vehicle at an accessible price point from a seller committed to clear, professional service.",
