      "description": "Looking for an affordable project, budget runabout, or handy spare car? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s got plenty of potential for the right buyer. A straightforward, honest car being offered at a sensible price \u2014 ideal for someone who doesn\u2019t mind giving it a bit of TLC. If you want something cheap with useful life left in it and room to make it your own, this could be a great fit.",
